declarations.comments:
`Blur` asserts that `s` and `t` are uniformly isomorphic to
`Day a x` and `Day b x` for some functor `x`.

Every `Blur` is also a `Hoist`.
declarations.title: Blur

declarations.comments:
`Pre` asserts that `s` and `t` are uniformly isomorphic to
`Compose x a` and `Compose x b` for some functor `x`.

Every `Pre` is also a `Hoist`.
declarations.title: Pre

declarations.comments:
`Post` asserts that `s` and `t` are uniformly isomorphic to
`Compose a x` and `Compose b x` for some functor `x`.

Every `Post` is also a `Hoist`.
declarations.title: Post

declarations.comments:
`Hoist` asserts that natural transformations between `a` and `b` can
be hoisted to natural transformations between `s` and `t`.
declarations.title: Hoist

declarations.comments: `StoreT s w` is uniformly isomorphic to `Day (Store s)`.
declarations.title: stored

declarations.comments: `TracedT t w` is uniformly isomorphic to `Day (Traced t)`.
declarations.title: traced

declarations.comments: `EnvT t w` is uniformly isomorphic to `Day (Env t)`.
declarations.title: envied

declarations.comments:
Profunctors which support lifting over compositions (on the left).

See "Monad Transformer Lenses" for details at
<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bxcz23GOJqc>.
declarations.title: Precomposed

declarations.comments: Profunctors which support lifting over compositions (on the right).
declarations.title: Postcomposed

declarations.comments:
Natural transformations, wrapped in a newtype to provide instances for
`Profunctor` and `Convoluted`.
declarations.title: Natural
